                {
                  "type": "text",
                  "text": " output parameter is used to indicate success or failure, but the procedure does not explicitly set it to 0 on successful completion, relying on the default behavior of the transaction block."
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
